,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"我都1516緊<br />\n兩個黃真係好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"太子巴打here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nall in黃國桐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"okkkk叫埋全屋投"},{"pid":"5ac0b760308ec3e357675ff81e12fca7732c7010","tid":1745512,"uid":120918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"btw藍營真係有樣睇<br />\n個丁健華賊眉賊眼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dc4489ef7c6af28801c4328ad0cc9be3425d91","tid":1745512,"uid":121994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"黃律師"},{"pid":"88cd7c87726040b8120f289f5f314452cda628e9","tid":1745512,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"防止𠝹票要做文宣"},{"pid":"13857ea4c7aea8392ca49d9693f536838786e8c0","tid":1745512,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:00:58.000Z","msg":"仲未明政府咩玩法既人留意<br />\n<br />\n你200萬+1人上街，佢屈9你20萬人<br />\n你5個月黎示威，佢屈你一少撮人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你只能夠講你計唔準，但佢可以話你都唔準，口同鼻拗</span><br />\n但係今次區選當公投，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係實打實既數字</span><br />\n＜就算對方種票，佢都要有身份證，影響既只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">地區議席分布，而唔係黃藍人數</span>＞<br />\n440幾萬選民，唔可能變500萬張選票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">宜家應該係煲大區選</span><br />\n   投建制派=支持止暴制亂<br />\n   投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n結果一出黎<br />\n黃票多過200萬，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再講一少撮人</span><br />\n藍票低過200萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">輪到我地屈佢一少撮人</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家係要煲大佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">   投建制派=支持止暴制亂 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">  投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉人數輸左=玻璃球打爛左</span><br />\n打爛左個玻璃球既後果係<br />\n1：運動失敗，逃亡潮開始<br />\n2：勇武轉化革命份子，引發更大暴力<br />\n3：香港政府管治失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果無更大暴力事件，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你都輸得甘心命抵啦，仲唔快手著草</span><br />\n輸唔起就係你起革命，唔係逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咪發傻阻礙區選，比個位政府入<br />\n話你地一少撮人唔願意面對現實<br />\n<br />\n如果區選人頭黃多過藍，你仲可以反口話政府唔願面對現實，實實在在既數字啊<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n目標唔係含投<br />\n係要打倒建制派，無黃議員都要推假獨立<br />\n刷低對方明面上議席，清除舊有垃圾<br />\n新垃圾到時先諗計清，推到班假獨立起碼對方可以做25仔/牆頭草，唔係宜家一面倒垃圾建制派<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔覺得係公投，對家都會煲大佢變公投<br />\n先發制人<br />\n咁樣先可以動員更多港豬<br />\n<br />\n我幾個上年紀既同事仲發傻諗住唔投票<br />\n要同佢講對家會當今次係公投，先on99夢醒<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n無證無據話對方做假，大陸吹一堆假消息已經玩爛個真相<br />\n<br />\n中共外國超多打手玩假英文消息<br />\n<br />\n你要證明一件事有問題，就係要你舉出證據<br />\n否則只會當你自欺欺人<br />\n雖然信你既人會好多，但係外國佬無辦法直接插手，無證據點放上枱啊<br />\n<br />\n你今次煲大佢，<br />\n一係對方唔做手腳<br />\n黃票真係多，我地贏<br />\n<br />\n一係對方做手腳<br />\n我地/外國捉到對方做手腳，我地都贏<br />\n<br />\n捉唔到對方做手腳，就到時做文宣講選舉有問題啦<br />\n結果都係返到去，無證據，對方信定唔信<br />\n<br />\n點玩都咁被動，點解唔認真d投票"},{"pid":"bb325fa7cc6a87afd2d37223dd4e56297d9046ee","tid":1745512,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"3號"},{"pid":"fadb0e39b53e764a1f5227a9cd79b902fe9d69dd","tid":1745512,"uid":310883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"黃國桐幫好多抗爭者打官司架大佬<br />\n仲癲過1號<br />\n白鴿黨入面有好多唔同類既人<br />\n唔好睇到白鴿就先入為主覺得係左膠"},{"pid":"1dfd2c7231060570f070249ef590f7e4777c2193","tid":1745512,"uid":222305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"394c6d2a24252496bd824c4af4acc974f2418e26","tid":1745512,"uid":222305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:11:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"357d5e597c5630e19465dac42471258b3ecb7b21","tid":1745512,"uid":222305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7c8cae42d52c3e629758525dd71c73d24ab4cadf","tid":1745512,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=4f7743e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=377e6890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=28b0cc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=eu0lilLN9Tj